text: Géza Tóth (22 February 1907 - 30 December 1990) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1990 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pécs
